  grammar:[
    {t:"Inversion",form:"Never/Rarely/Hardly + aux + sujeto",ex:["Never have I seen such a mess. | Nunca he visto semejante desorden.","Rarely do I get this chance. | Rara vez tengo esta oportunidad.","Hardly had I arrived when it started. | Apenas había llegado cuando empezó.","Not only did she win, she broke a record. | No solo ganó, batió un récord.","Little did he know. | Poco sabía él."]},
