    {t:"Subjunctive",form:"suggest/recommend (that) + base",ex:["I suggest he be on time. | Sugiero que llegue a tiempo.","I recommend that she take a break. | Recomiendo que ella tome un descanso.","They insist that he stay. | Insisten en que se quede.","It's vital that we act. | Es vital que actuemos.","I demand that it be fixed. | Exijo que se arregle."]},
