    {t:"Verbos tipo gustar",form:"fascinar, encantar, molestar, doler, parecer + me/te/le/nos/les",ex:["Me encanta la música. | I love music.","¿Te molesta el ruido? | Does the noise bother you?","Me duele la cabeza. | My head hurts.","A ella le fascina leer. | She's fascinated by reading.","¿Qué te parece? | What do you think?"]}
