    {t:"Subject pronouns",form:"je, tu, il/elle/on, nous, vous, ils/elles",ex:["Je suis américain/e. | I am American.","Tu parles anglais. | You speak English.","Il/Elle est sympa. | He/She is nice.","Nous habitons ici. | We live here.","Vous êtes de New York. | You are from New York."]},
