    {t:"Adverbes de fréquence",form:"toujours, souvent, parfois, rarement, jamais",ex:["Je prends toujours mon café. | I always have my coffee.","On mange souvent dehors. | We often eat out.","Tu arrives parfois en retard. | You sometimes arrive late.","Elle regarde rarement la télé. | She rarely watches TV.","Je ne fume jamais. | I never smoke."]},
