  writing:["Argue for or against remote work in French.","Describe a turning point in your life.","Write a film review using relative clauses.","Rewrite a dialogue in reported speech (discours indirect).","Write a hypothetical: si + imparfait + conditionnel."],
  speaking:["Debate with yourself: 2 points for and 2 against a topic.","Tell an anecdote mixing passé composé and imparfait.","Shadow a French speaker for 30 seconds.","Describe what you'd do if you won the lottery.","Give opinion and qualify it (malgré, cependant)."],
