  writing:["Write a formal opinion essay intro in French with a nuanced argument.","Argue a controversial point, then give the counterargument.","Summarize a complex idea using formal connectors (néanmoins, par conséquent).","Write about a past regret using si + plus-que-parfait + conditionnel passé.","Use nominalisation: turn 3 verb phrases into formal noun phrases."],
